# Project memory (ported from Claude Code)

Persistent context for this repo lives in `memory-bank/` — one markdown file per
fact. This file is the always-loaded index. When a task touches a topic below,
READ the linked file in `memory-bank/` before acting; do not rely on the
one-line hook alone. Keep these notes updated as work lands, and add a new
`memory-bank/<slug>.md` file plus an index line here when you learn something
durable that isn't derivable from the code or git history.

`memory-bank/` is gitignored — it is local-only and may contain sensitive
operational detail (server, token, and pilot notes). Do not paste its contents
into commits, PRs, or anything that leaves this machine.

## Working preferences
- Run high/xhigh effort with verification discipline; verify via grep/pgrep and
  real output, not by eye. (see operating-mode-fable-parity)
- Desktop app aesthetic: dark/glassy, not flat-light/blocky. (see threshold-ui-design-direction)

